<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[اللِّحْية]</span>: معروفة، <span class="c2">(قال اللّاه تعالى:<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لاا تَأْخُذْ بِلِحْيَتِي <span class="c2">«١»</span>) <span class="c2">«٢»</span> والجميع:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
